    'The main exhibition hall of Tianfu Agricultural Expo Park',
    'The Tianfu Agricultural Expo Park project is located in Xingyi Town, Xinjin County and Sanjiang Town, Chongzhou City, close to Chengxinpu Expressway and Chengdu Second Ring Expressway, with good landscape and traffic conditions. The main exhibition hall is located in the agriculture exhibition area, north of Chengxin Pu Expressway and west of the Yangma River, with a land area of about 135,000 square meters. It includes the functions of agricultural exhibition hall, conference center, Tianfu Agricultural Civilization Museum, cultural and creative incubation, characteristic commercial neighborhood, outdoor exhibition space and other functions, with a total construction area of about 132,000 square meters. The project uses five arched scaffolding to interpenetrate with the surrounding pastoral landscape, and adopts prefabricated steel and wood structure scaffolding combined with colorful ETFE enclosure system to create a semi-outdoor non-energy consumption space, embodies the concept of green development and environmentally friendly design. Ecological energy-saving. 
The plan adopts a finger-shaped penetration layout pattern, which is mutually infiltrated with the pastoral landscape. At the same time, in order to reflect the characteristics of the agricultural expo exhibition and take into account the basic needs of wind and rain shelter, it mainly adopts the form of an outdoor exhibition venue with a roof. Through appropriate passive green building technology, the organization of air flow is guided to create a comfortable semi-outdoor activity space. The exhibition part has achieved the goal of near-zero energy consumption, truly realizing the green ecological concept that is in line with the agricultural expo. The design of the building opening effectively organizes the air flow to form a ventilation corridor, so that the indoor temperature can be kept in a more comfortable state for a long time. The microclimate environment of human activities has been greatly improved. In addition, fog spraying additional measures are used at a close range to regulate the micro-environment.
Wooden frame. 
The architectural form is a large-span structure, combined with the fact that the project is located in farmland, abandoning the reinforced concrete structure form that causes greater damage to farmland during construction and is not renewable. Laminated wood structure is a negative carbon material that can be carbon-fixed. It can better reflect ecological and agricultural characteristics and is all factory-processed. On-site assembly reduces construction errors and ensures completion quality. At the same time, wooden structures originate from nature, with simple colors and in line with agricultural expo characteristics.
Colorful film. 
ETFE film material is light in weight, good in light transmission, easy to color, and can be matched with colorful fields through colorful textures to better reflect agricultural expo concepts.
Implanted nature.
 In order to introduce landscape into the arch shed and create an outdoor pastoral feeling indoors, at the boundary, while the building extends into the field, it also extends the external landscape environment into the arch shed to blur and weaken the boundary between architecture and nature and increase opportunities for all-weather contact with nature.',
