4 strips (with 7 oscillating sensors each) x 6,700 kW = 26.8 MW
High Concentration Photovoltaics Panels x 2,600 kW  = 2.6 MW
2 OTEC Systems (Ocean Thermal Energy Conversion) x 10,500 kW = 21 MW
Total power: 103.6 MW on-board electricity supply',
